{"tid":327026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日雨量集中係東部 新界北部水浸特別報告 有乜野用???","createTime":"2017-07-18T12:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T12:51:50.000Z","uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4804864c71041e752afa5cf6c1b678d2255ec1ed","tid":327026,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/18/202823_cddcdcf2aa788d98fb83497827d2d8cc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F18%2F202823_cddcdcf2aa788d98fb83497827d2d8cc.png&h=72d9574b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新界北部水浸特別報告<br />\n<br />\n香港天文台在7月18日下午5時正發出之新界北部水浸特別報告。<br />\n<br />\n新界北部，尤其是八鄉及錦田一帶，正受大雨影響。在過去1小時，該區錄得超過60毫米雨量。<br />\n<br />\n新界北部可能受大雨影響之市民，應採取適當的預防措施，以防止水浸可能引致的損失。大雨可能引致山洪暴發，市民應遠離河道。鄉村附近若有防洪警鐘，村民亦應留意。<br />\n<br />\n以上天氣稿由天文台於2017年07月18日17時00分發出<br />\n<br />\n明明八鄉及錦田一帶係全港雨量最少既地方<br />\n而所有傳媒都係報緊西貢大埔水浸<br />\n呢個垃圾警告係咪不合時直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天文台做野係咪是是但但<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c4980da4e00087940454e47d8f131404b029d0","tid":327026,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"點解唔直接改制做水浸警告<br />\n雖然傳統黎講 元朗盆地係易D水浸<br />\n但係都唔係求鳩其其copy出黎下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3f9998c860e5b1cb92b490dfa99e8404f58936","tid":327026,"uid":72590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56972864&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56972864%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170718&d=DzMzOM2mnx81MO0OqNJGopUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=69ec1353\" data-ef-url=\"https:/